1
00:00:00,863 --> 00:00:04,261
I like this television very much.
我非常喜欢这台电视机.

2
00:00:04,262 --> 00:00:07,011
How much does it cost?
请问它多少钱?

3
00:00:07,342 --> 00:00:11,737
It's the most expensive model in the shop.
这是店里最贵的型号.

4
00:00:11,738 --> 00:00:15,239
It costs five hundred pounds.
它的售价是500英镑.

5
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:18,978
That's too expensive for us.
这对我们来说太贵了.

6
00:00:19,032 --> 00:00:22,855
We can't afford all that money.
我们花不起那么多钱.

7
00:00:23,079 --> 00:00:27,144
This model's less expensive than that one.
这种型号比那种要便宜些.

8
00:00:27,145 --> 00:00:30,353
It's only three hundred pounds.
它只要300英镑.

9
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:36,946
But, of course, it's not as good as the expensive one.
但是,它当然没有价钱高的那种好.

10
00:00:36,947 --> 00:00:39,978
I don't like this model.
我不喜欢这种型号.

11
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:46,567
The other model's more expensive, but it's worth the money.
那种型号价格是贵一些,但它值这么多钱.

12
00:00:47,032 --> 00:00:50,856
Can we buy it on instalments?
我们可以用分期付款的方式购买吗?

13
00:00:50,857 --> 00:00:57,203
Of course. You can pay a deposit of thirty pounds,
当然可以.您可以先付30英镑定金.

14
00:00:57,204 --> 00:01:02,806
and then fourteen pounds a month for three years.
然后每月14镑,3年付清.

15
00:01:03,259 --> 00:01:05,724
Do you like it, dear?
你喜欢吗,亲爱的?

16
00:01:06,556 --> 00:01:12,603
I certainly do, but I don't like the price.
我当然喜欢,但是我不喜欢这个价钱.

17
00:01:12,989 --> 00:01:19,737
You always want the best, but we can't afford it.
你总是要买最好的,可我们买不起.

18
00:01:20,995 --> 00:01:26,498
Sometimes you think you're a millionaire!
有时候你认为自己是个百万富翁!

19
00:01:26,499 --> 00:01:30,917
Millionaires don't buy things on instalments!
百万富翁是不会分期付款买东西的!

